Name:           m17n-db
Version:        1.8.0
Release:        0
Summary:        Database Needed by the m17n Library m17n-lib
License:        GPL-2.0-or-later AND LGPL-2.1-or-later AND SUSE-Public-Domain AND MIT
Group:          System/I18n/Japanese
URL:            https://www.m17n.org/m17n-lib/
